                  src="public/assets/img/about/about.jpg"
                  alt="about
                  thumb"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div className="col-lg-7">
              <div className="about-content">
                <h2 className="about-title">About Us</h2>
                <p>
                  Mr. Ashok Zinzuwadia started the journey with a small
                  wholesale unit of gold jewelry in soni bazar of Rajkot city in
                  Gujarat with his father Mr. Mathurdas Zinzuwadia. Later In the
                  beginning of the year 1987 he closed down the wholesale unit.
                </p>
                <p>
                  He then established Radhika Jewellers in 1987, The journey of
                  retail based selling started from 2nd October 1987 with a
                  small jewelry shop of 200 sq. ft. with just 7 employees and
                  small amount of (appx.) 15 kg of gold jewelry stock. Later in
                  the year 1995 Mr.Haresh Zinzuwadia brother of Mr. Ashok joined
                  the family business.
                </p>
                <p>
                  Radhika Jewellers was a proprietary firm till 30th June 2014
                  under the proprietorship of Mr. Ashok Zinzuwadia. From June
                  2014 the firm was converted to a partnership firm with 7
                  partners and Public Limited Company with effect from 22nd July
                  2016.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
